For converting gff file to gtf AGAT tool was used (https://github.com/NBISweden/AGAT)

Following steps were used

#Docker image was pulled for agat version 0.9.1
docker pull quay.io/biocontainers/agat:0.9.1--pl5321hdfd78af_0 


docker run -v ${PWD}:/agat quay.io/biocontainers/agat:0.9.1--pl5321hdfd78af_0 agat_convert_sp_gff2gtf.pl --gff agat/bison.liftoff.gff -o /Users/hxo752/Desktop/bison.liftoff.gtf
 
